# Dougs Plugin Config

Copy this file to `.claude/dougs.local.md` in your project root, then fill in your company info.

To find your `company_id`: log into app.dougs.fr, the URL contains `/c/<ID>/...` — that's your company_id.

The sections below populate the footer/header of your quotes (legal mentions, contact, payment terms). Edit them to match your company.

